{"tid":503120,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)KISSASS1-2 天賦的禮物","createTime":"2017-12-18T14:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T16:12:32.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2b3204e3156151ba6b1331fc1f0f5d50341e1b4a","tid":503120,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T14:14:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=uhb2jV%2FeVWKqnXQ%2FwAnWh26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e789998c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=uhb2jV%2FeVWKqnXQ%2FwAnWh26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=71b6d415\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/30/Kick-Ass_film_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F30%2FKick-Ass_film_poster.jpg&h=f16cf64b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/56/Kick-Ass2-Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F56%2FKick-Ass2-Poster.jpg&h=9516d1fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1平凡無奇的青少年戴夫&middot;萊佐斯基（Dave Lizewski，亞倫&middot;強森飾）想知道在現實生活中，為何沒人想成為漫畫裡的超級英雄。他與好友在被惡霸劫奪時，旁觀者卻無所作為，戴夫決心成為一個真實的超級英雄。他從eBay買件綠色緊身衣作為服裝，裝扮成打擊犯罪的蒙面英雄，儘管沒有任何超能力及接受各種訓練..<br />\n<br />\n2.戴夫&middot;萊佐斯基（亞倫&middot;強森 飾）不再以「屌爆俠」身份打擊犯罪後過上了無聊的生活，開始接受「超殺女」明蒂&middot;麥奎迪（克蘿伊&middot;摩蕾茲 飾）的訓練成為英雄角色。意外殺死母親的克里斯&middot;達米柯（克里斯托福&middot;敏茲-普雷斯 飾）被家族的錢控制，將自己重塑為超級惡棍「臭B王」，發誓要報復屌爆俠。監護人馬庫斯（莫里斯&middot;錢雷諾 飾）發現明蒂仍在打擊罪犯，要她發誓放棄這種行為。戴夫的女友凱蒂&middot;多瑪（琳德茜&middot;馮塞卡 飾）已經注意到戴夫的怪異行為，認為他跟明蒂（她告訴凱蒂自己曾騙過戴夫）聯手欺騙他，於是跟他分手..<br />\n<br />\n3.在一座佛羅里達州中部的小鎮，七歲的瑪麗在她入學的第一天展現卓越的數學天份。她獲得一筆獎學金供她到專收天才兒童的私立學校就讀，但他的舅舅拒絕接受。他之所以如此，乃因瑪麗的母親曾經是極有前途的數學家，自殺之前致力於納維&ndash;斯托克斯問題（尚未被破解千禧年大獎難題之一）當時瑪麗六個月大。從那時起她的舅舅法蘭克便擔任瑪麗實際上的監護人。他堅信他的妹妹會希望瑪麗過「正常的」童年..<br />\n<br />\n10 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=uhb2jV%2FeVWKqnXQ%2FwAnWh26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=0258d480\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=uhb2jV%2FeVWKqnXQ%2FwAnWh26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=b461ae3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae809d1a8a1c86282bf090a72cd3bf445610c3e","tid":503120,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T14:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3a9e32241e9178cd5b94f83e6f06cd2f133115","tid":503120,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T14:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca314d714674a7af8e30ca2561063